That spans the cloud control plane, the Linux/server fundamentals underneath, and the application-layer patterns on top. For day-to-day DevOps work, the highest-leverage areas are VPC/subnet/security-group design, the diagnostic tool belt (dig, ss, tcpdump, curl), TLS, load balancing, and Kubernetes/service-mesh networking.